			At MangoAGS, we are always clear and transparent about career opportunities for every member who joins us. 
			Not only do we provide a specific training roadmap, but we also outline detailed career advancement plans 
			for each position. This enables every member to strive and grow through each level.
		</p>
		<p class="text-2xl font-bold leading-relaxed">
			Here, in addition to honing your core professional skills, you will also have the opportunity to develop 
			leadership abilities and improve yourself every day. Furthermore, MangoAGS is committed to fostering 
			happiness, purpose, and life enjoyment - not just focusing on work alone.
		</p>
